user.bio: “La perfection est atteinte, non pas lorsqu'il n'y a plus rien à ajouter, mais lorsqu'il n'y a plus rien à retirer.”

commit.title: [ci] Build full developments as time limits are larger in Gitlab.
commit.message:
[ci] Build full developments as time limits are larger in Gitlab.

In the original Travis CI setup, job time limit was an issue. However,
the migration to Gitlab has much improved this problem due to a) Coq
not being built, b) time limits are in general much larger.

We thus disable the expensive builds from Travis and instruct Gitlab
to build such developments [fiat-crypto, geocoq, math-comp, unimath,
vst] in full.
